flowchart TD
    A([AWS account activity])

    A --> CT[CloudTrail]
    A --> GD[GuardDuty<br/>managed threat detection]

    CT --> S3[(S3<br/>audit evidence)]
    CT --> CW1[CloudWatch Logs<br/>investigation logs]

    GD --> SH[Security Hub<br/>centralized findings dashboard]
    GD --> EB{EventBridge rule<br/>severity &ge; 7}

    EB --> SNS[SNS<br/>SOC analyst email]
    EB --> LMB[Lambda<br/>incident parsing<br/>+ response logging]

    LMB --> CW2[CloudWatch Logs<br/>responder output]

    classDef detect fill:#fde68a,stroke:#a16207,color:#000
    classDef route  fill:#c7d2fe,stroke:#3730a3,color:#000
    classDef store  fill:#bbf7d0,stroke:#166534,color:#000
    classDef alert  fill:#fecaca,stroke:#991b1b,color:#000
    class GD,SH detect
    class EB route
    class S3,CW1,CW2 store
    class SNS,LMB alert
